{"tid":1236230,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"本人最接受唔到嘅就係7婆嘅“母親論”你仲當唔當香港係民主社會?","createTime":"2019-06-17T11:25:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T03:35:10.000Z","uid":221105,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f673f4bf23c276d645689540f2ab207d9c9a6148","tid":1236230,"uid":221105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:25:57.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;母親論&rdquo;News(只看蘋果，不看CCTVB): 【引渡惡法】逾萬名香港媽媽聯署轟林鄭：我們不會以武力對待孩子 - <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190613/59710136\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190613%2F59710136&d=yUf3ZniyPWjB5eI%2FQURZCgQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=ae1c8553\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190613%2F59710136&h=b82168b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190613/59710136</a> <br />\n<br />\n如果你仲當香港係一個民主社會，咁林鄭你提出&ldquo;母親論&rdquo;嘅嗰一刻開始，就應該要落台。<br />\n<br />\n雖然林鄭你平時睇開百度，但都係俾返wiki嘅link你:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你知唔知乜嘢係&ldquo;民主&rdquo;?</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/民主\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB&d=yUf3ZniyPWjB5eI%2FQURZCgQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=3f485cad\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/民主</a><br />\n總括而言，&ldquo;民主&rdquo;係指<span style=\"color: violet;\">由人民統治國家，應&ldquo;以民為本&rdquo;</span>，並非<span style=\"color: maroon;\">由總統/領導人</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">統治/<span style=\"font-size: large;\">照顧</span></span><span style=\"color: maroon;\">人民</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<code>各位巴打絲打，你明唔明點解我接受唔到7婆咁講?</code><br />\n<br />\n民主社會嘅總統/領導人，應該係會聆聽人民嘅意見，經過諮詢同投票之後先會實行。我承認咩都投票係會嚴重減慢香港嘅發展，會一事無成。但連民意都未聽就做，就會變咗做&ldquo;統治&rdquo;，亦即係好似<strong>極權主義國家</strong>同<strong>共產主義國家</strong>咁...一個人決定哂所有嘢，掌控哂全部嘅人民。<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>重申: 香港<del><strong>依家仲</strong></del>係民主社會，<strong>應該係</strong>由人民統治，唔應該係由林鄭&ldquo;照顧&rdquo;我哋。如果佢比喻自已做&ldquo;母親&rdquo;，我哋係佢嘅兒女，啫係<span style=\"color: red;\">佢已經唔當香港係民主社會</span>。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本人都好同意港媽們&ldquo;我們不會以武力對待孩子&rdquo;嘅講法，只不過我嘅重點係林鄭唔再當香港係民主嘅社會，只係聽完北京指示之後，&ldquo;照顧&rdquo;香港700幾萬市民<br />\n<br />\nbtw祝 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭早日落台</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />認同請分享+正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Sorry講嘢1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"28c9576a7d14303721ffcb5e9024b4c6af6ed6e4","tid":1236230,"uid":221105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:46:50.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f31188145f73d41f5d01cce887b30654adf35c","tid":1236230,"uid":79471,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:47:56.000Z","msg":"漢人嗰種垃撚圾父母官概念"},{"pid":"57a6dae07ebc4710ad99cfdc6da55545e5ba4e87","tid":1236230,"uid":221105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:17:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"147383900ccb4f9cdb1301f665f0348f07f8817c","tid":1236230,"uid":221105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:40:30.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5754aaf2adebb8453759e98383e54fb86dc2008f","tid":1236230,"uid":221105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:48:48.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26aaec7eef4bfa897be80cb03b86d157